VIKI
===============

This is Viki, our bot.

Viki is in charge of all automated operations within our community,  
from sending alerts and emails to voting in elections and verifying rocket launch codes.

It contains integrated System and Public APIs for managing the ecosystem.

To contribute, please raise a pull request.  
Proper documentation and programming practices are a MUST!  
If in doubt, ASK!

You can get in contact with us via:

    connect@byte-beam.io

